      <p>Our quiz evaluates 12 key lifestyle factors — from your living space and activity level to grooming tolerance and work schedule — and scores each against a database of 30+ popular dog breeds. Each breed has a detailed profile covering size, energy, grooming needs, trainability, noise level, shedding, and more.</p>
      <p>Your answers are weighted and compared against each breed's characteristics to produce a compatibility percentage. The result is a personalized ranking of breeds most likely to thrive in your specific situation.</p>

